<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout fade-in">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label">About me</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Architect, engineer<br />and builder.</h2>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            My background is computational physics. Over the past decade I've moved
            between academia and industry — running R&D for Brazil's largest restaurant
            chain, designing knowledge graphs for a biotech MSc, and now directing
            crisis-management AI in Vienna.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm most useful at the boundary where research meets a shipping deadline —
            the kind of work where you need someone who can read the paper
            and write the deployment config.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-inline: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .about-layout {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about .section-label,
  .about .section-title {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .about .section-label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

</style>
